Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Download fails with SSL error

# Use --insecure flag (for lab environment only)
curl --insecure -o data/file.csv "URL"
Issue: CSV parsing errors

Check for comment lines starting with '#'
Verify file encoding: file -i data/filename.csv
Use errors='ignore' when opening files
Issue: Empty or missing data

Verify downloads completed: ls -lh data/
Check file contents: head -20 data/filename.csv
Ensure processing script limits are set (50 records per source)
Issue: LibreOffice won't open

# Kill existing processes
killall soffice.bin
# Try again
libreoffice --calc output/file.csv &
Issue: JSON formatting errors

Validate JSON: python3 -m json.tool output/file.json
Check for proper dictionary/list structures
Ensure all strings are properly quoted
